<chapter id="help" xreflabel="Using PDB2PQR">
<title>Using PDB2PQR</title>

<simplesect>
<title>Using PDB2PQR roll</title>

<para>
Simply run PDB2PQR on your server:
</para>

<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>directly as a <ulink url="http://rollhost/opal2/dashboard?command=serviceList">web service</ulink> 
</para></listitem>
<listitem><para>through <ulink url="http://rollhost/pdb2pqr">CGI interface</ulink> 
</para></listitem>
</itemizedlist>

</simplesect>

<simplesect> 
